These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: swimming, cricket, badminton
1. Sport:cricket is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far right##1
3. Sport:swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | badminton | cricket | swimming |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: lemon, pineapple, pumpkin
1. Food:pineapple is in an odd position##4
2. Food:lemon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | lemon | pumpkin | pineapple |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: video-games, hiking, skydiving
1. Hobby:hiking is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:hiking is on the left or right of Hobby:skydiving##3
3. Hobby:skydiving is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | video-games | hiking | skydiving |

 #################################
 
